SUMMARY:Tools for Tough Times
DESCRIPTION:Struggling to cope? This&#160\;4 week series teaches basic co
 ping skills for various challenges commonly faced by college students. Af
 ter education\, students will be invited to talk about their experiences 
 with the topic of the week and share if they have any skills that have wo
 rked for them thus far.  &#160\;  Topics:  April 9 - Stress  April 16 - M
 ental Health  April 23 - Time Management  April 30 - Emotional Regulation
   &#160\;  Join this discussion group at the LGBTQ+ Culture Center to gai
 n some tools for tough times!  &#160\;All Indiana University events\, gro
 ups\, activities\, and educational\, cultural\, and historical observance
 s welcome all IU students and other members of the Indiana University com
 munity.
